          "prompt_html": "<h1>MULTIPLE CHOICE 14</h1><p><strong>Questions 16 - 20</strong></p><p>Choose the correct letter, <strong>A, B or C</strong>.</p><p><strong>Westley Youth Centre - Evening Activities</strong></p><p>16 The Youth Centre's theatre workshop ...</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    ... is free to join.</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    ... lasts for 2 hours.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    ... puts on shows in a theatre in town.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>17 The Youth Centre's film evenings ...</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    ... take place every week.</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    ... show the latest film releases.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    ... are sponsored by a local film rental business.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>18 The Youth Centre's discos ...</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    ... cost nothing extra for Youth Centre members.</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    ... feature a professional disc jockey.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    ... are run under adult supervision.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>19 If any child repeatedly misbehaves ...</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    ... they will be warned.</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    ... the Youth Centre will contact their parents.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    ... they will be banned from entry to the Youth Centre for 1 month.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>20 Information about the Youth Centre can be found ...</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    ... in the Youth Centre leaflets.</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    ... on the Youth Centre website.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    ... in both the Youth Centre's leaflets and its website.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>",
